name: About Lines #3: Elevation
description:
After the colouring, the elevation. Lifting the factual to another level, thoughts and actions becoming one.

This piece is part of a series inspired by Japanese calligraphy and the works of German-French painter Hans Hartung (1904 - 1989).

PNG, 2960 × 1850 px · Original artwork by Andreas Rau · Oslo, 2021
